document_data.name: Jhalikoe
document_data.mainbody: '''Jhalikoe''' was a [[Cormyte]] noble guest at the [[Open Feast]] of {{yearlink|1479}}.
document_data.Relationships: They were on a first name basis with the envoy from [[Milvarune]] at the [[Open Feast]], despite them having been recently arrived to Cormyr.
document_data.History: Jhalikoe participated in the Open Feast held at [[Castle Obarskyr]] on [[Mirtul 26]] of the {{yearlinkName|1479}}, where they briefly entertained the envoy from [[Milvarune]], discussing subjects such as the [[Silent Shadow]], [[Skult]], and [[Vandarl]].
